entries.femaleVariant: Hey, V! It's Blue Moon from Us Cracks... Y'know, the band...?
Happy to help.
I'm sorry, but now's not really a good time.
How do you know the threat's real and not just a joke in poor taste?
Now's not a good time.
How do you know if the threat is real?
Happy to help out.
Whole of Night City knows you. What's crackin'?
Mean you're not calling to ask me to be your backup dancer? Just... just kidding. What can I do you for?
entries.maleVariant: What, you mean you're not calling me to ask me to be your backup dancer? Just kidding. What can I do you for?

entries.femaleVariant: V... That last letter I got was a bomb. Security got to it first, of course, but... Ehh, you see what I'm dealing with?
Can't your bandmates do something?
Can't your bandmates do anything about it? You seem like a bunch of girls who can take care of themselves.
entries.maleVariant: Well, can't your bandmates do anything about it? You seem like a bunch of girls who can take care of themselves.

entries.femaleVariant: V... I don't even know what this guy looks like! We need to catch him in the act. But, like, quietly.
As for us... You said it yourself – whole city knows our faces.
Dammit, V...!
V? Oh, thank god you called! I got another letter – he said he wants to wear my face as a mask...! Y-You've gotta help me!
Phew. Kerry was right – you're, like, super chill.
So, I've got a plan. I'll go for a little stroll by Kabuki Roundabout, while you hang back – watch out for any signs of trouble.
You catch something suspicious... Like, if you see the guy... and you're a hundred per cent sure it's him...
I'll know what to do.
No, no, wait, we're not killing anyone here! That would be bad for the band's, like, PR and stuff. All we wanna do is teach him a lesson.
I've... got a problem...
Whatever. You make the rules.
It's about a fan of mine. The, um... the weirder variety.
I can't just wait around till something bad happens. We have to find him, and... and deal with him.
Uh-huh. Doesn't get more real than that.
I mean, I'm sure you've got your reasons and everything, but... Just call me if you change your mind, OK? Please.
I've been getting death threats. A lot of 'em. All sent to my private address. I'm also being followed.
Awesome! So just go to Kabuki, sit on the bench and wait for me. I'll come to you.
Do you know anything about him?
Our guy – you know anything about him?
Nothing. Only that he signs his letters "GC."
Hm. Not much to go on... Clue, nonetheless.
entries.maleVariant: Huh. Not much to go on... It's a clue, nonetheless.

entries.femaleVariant: [Sit]
I don't know how much you charge, V... but I'm prepared to pay whatever the cost – believe me.
